{"id":234111,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/06/维权网-北京警方为阻止访民学电脑半夜抓走胡俊/","date":"2012-06-23T02:01:06Z","modified":"2012-06-23T02:01:06Z","title":"维权网 | 北京警方为阻止访民学电脑半夜抓走胡俊雄","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'> </a>（维权网信息员方芳、孙小芸报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">23</span><span>日零点</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">40</span><span>分</span><span>，湖北民主人士胡俊雄在北京寿保庄北站附近出租房内被</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>余名北京国保和警察抓走。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span> </p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据知情人透露，几天前，有人在一个访民电脑爱好者聚集的群里发出通知：端午节（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">23</span><span>日</span><span>）请大家吃粽子，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>、自带水杯；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>、笔记本；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>、笔记本电脑；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>、注意秩序。并列出了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>个具体联系人的姓名。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>虽然很简单的几句话，大家都心照不宣非常高兴，明白是在端午节举办访民电脑培训活动，此前已经成功举办过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>期，访民学习电脑的热情都非常高，每次都有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">100-200</span><span>人参加。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>胡俊雄精通电脑技术，经常帮访民朋友维修电脑，讲授电脑知识，他热情周到，百问不厌，深受访民的尊敬，此次胡俊雄打算在端午节再次为访民举办电脑知识培训，可能此次活动被当局察觉，害怕他向访民讲授电脑知识。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据了解，带走胡俊雄的是北京市公安局大兴分局金星派出所的警察，他们首先查看了胡俊雄的身份证，确认身份后将他抓走。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>信息员拨打了胡俊雄的手机，提示为关机。随后又拨打金星派出所电话，接线警员说不知道情况。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>胡俊雄：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15611248264</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>金星派出所：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">010-61285666</span><span>，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">010-61286293</span></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-6426291575696265632?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18269,20534],"tags":[16910,19196]}